  Ms MILLER-FROST

 (
Boothby
) (
10:10
):  I rise today to speak to the National Redress Scheme for Institutional Child Sexual Abuse Amendment Bill 2023. This bill introduces legislative amendments to the National Redress Scheme for Institutional Child Sexual Abuse Act 2018. These amendments form part of the government's final response to recommendations from the Final report—second year review of the National Redress Scheme, a review undertaken by Ms Robyn Kruk AO.
